      "type": "feat",
      "img": "icons/magic/perception/eye-ringed-green.webp",
      "system": {
        "description": {
          "value": "<p>Your deity rewards you with hazy visions of things to come. Each time you earn 1 or more Milestones, you earn an equal number of fate points. Whenever you or a creature within 10 feet makes a test, you can spend 1 fate point to tap into a vision of the outcome, granting that creature an advantage on the test. You lose any remaining fate points when you finish a long rest.</p>",
          "chat": ""
